title: Alabama corrections officer who escaped with inmate has died in hospital, sheriff says - CNN

description: Alabama corrections officer Vicky White has died due to her injuries, Sheriff Dave Wedding of Vanderburgh County told CNN. She and escaped Alabama inmate Casey White were taken into custody following a chase in Indiana, authorities said late Monday.
